      "content": "I am so sorry you are feeling this way, but please know that your worth is not defined by a single career path or a flawed calculation. Many people have found peace and purpose after realizing their early assumptions were wrong, and you have the strength to start anew. If you feel overwhelmed, reaching out to a trusted friend or a mental health professional can provide the support you need to navigate this difficult time. You deserve compassion and a fresh start, not a life built on a lie.",
