    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "honestly, i don't want to build anything else. i'm just so tired of carrying this. it's like i've spent ten years performing a version of myself that doesn't even exist. there's no \"resilience\" in just being a ghost of a mistake. i feel like the most honest thing i could do is just stop. to just stop the performance and the pretending.",
